40static long dispatchQueueIdentifier(WorkQueue::QOS qos)
41{
42 switch (qos) {
43 case WorkQueue::QOS::UserInteractive:
44 case WorkQueue::QOS::UserInitiated:
45 case WorkQueue::QOS::Default:
46 return DISPATCH_QUEUE_PRIORITY_DEFAULT;
47 case WorkQueue::QOS::Utility:
48 return DISPATCH_QUEUE_PRIORITY_LOW;
49 case WorkQueue::QOS::Background:
50 return DISPATCH_QUEUE_PRIORITY_BACKGROUND;
51 }
52}
53
54IOChannel::IOChannel(const String& filePath, Type type, std::optional<WorkQueue::QOS> qos)
55 : m_path(filePath)
56 , m_type(type)
57{
58 auto path = FileSystem::fileSystemRepresentation(filePath);
59 int oflag;
60 mode_t mode;
61 WorkQueue::QOS dispatchQOS;
62
63 switch (m_type) {
64 case Type::Create:
65 // We don't want to truncate any existing file (with O_TRUNC) as another thread might be mapping it.
66 unlink(path.data());
67 oflag = O_RDWR | O_CREAT | O_NONBLOCK;
68 mode = S_IRUSR | S_IWUSR;
69 dispatchQOS = qos.value_or(WorkQueue::QOS::Background);
70 break;
71 case Type::Write:
72 oflag = O_WRONLY | O_NONBLOCK;
73 mode = S_IRUSR | S_IWUSR;
74 dispatchQOS = qos.value_or(WorkQueue::QOS::Background);
75 break;
76 case Type::Read:
77 oflag = O_RDONLY | O_NONBLOCK;
78 mode = 0;
79 dispatchQOS = qos.value_or(WorkQueue::QOS::Default);
80 }
81
82 int fd = ::open(path.data(), oflag, mode);
83 m_fileDescriptor = fd;
84
85 m_dispatchIO = adoptOSObject(dispatch_io_create(DISPATCH_IO_RANDOM, fd, dispatch_get_global_queue(dispatchQueueIdentifier(dispatchQOS), 0), [fd](int) {
86 close(fd);
87 }));
88 ASSERT(m_dispatchIO.get());
89
90 // This makes the channel read/write all data before invoking the handlers.
91 dispatch_io_set_low_water(m_dispatchIO.get(), std::numeric_limits<size_t>::max());
92}
93
94IOChannel::~IOChannel()
95{
96 RELEASE_ASSERT(!m_wasDeleted.exchange(true));
97}
98
99void IOChannel::read(size_t offset, size_t size, WorkQueue& queue, Function<void (Data&, int error)>&& completionHandler)
100{
101 RefPtr<IOChannel> channel(this);
102 bool didCallCompletionHandler = false;
103 dispatch_io_read(m_dispatchIO.get(), offset, size, queue.dispatchQueue(), makeBlockPtr([channel, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler), didCallCompletionHandler](bool done, dispatch_data_t fileData, int error) mutable {
104 ASSERT_UNUSED(done, done || !didCallCompletionHandler);
105 if (didCallCompletionHandler)
106 return;
107 Data data { OSObjectPtr<dispatch_data_t> { fileData } };
108 auto callback = WTFMove(completionHandler);
109 callback(data, error);
110 didCallCompletionHandler = true;
111 }).get());
112}
113
114void IOChannel::write(size_t offset, const Data& data, WorkQueue& queue, Function<void (int error)>&& completionHandler)
115{
116 RefPtr<IOChannel> channel(this);
117 auto dispatchData = data.dispatchData();
118 dispatch_io_write(m_dispatchIO.get(), offset, dispatchData, queue.dispatchQueue(), makeBlockPtr([channel, completionHandler = WTFMove(completionHandler)](bool done, dispatch_data_t fileData, int error) mutable {
119 ASSERT_UNUSED(done, done);
120 auto callback = WTFMove(completionHandler);
121 callback(error);
122 }).get());
123}
